# College ERP — UML Diagrams

All diagrams generated from analysis of both `College_ERP/backend` and `frontend/app`.

---

## 1. ER / Class Diagram — Database Schema

```mermaid
classDiagram
    direction LR

    class department {
        +int department_id PK
        +varchar department_code UK
        +varchar department_name UK
    }

    class teachers {
        +int teacher_id PK
        +varchar first_name
        +varchar last_name
        +varchar email UK
        +varchar password
        +enum role : admin | faculty
        +varchar primary_phone
        +varchar alternate_phone
        +int department_id FK
        +varchar designation
    }

    class students {
        +int student_id PK
        +varchar first_name
        +varchar middle_name
        +varchar last_name
        +date DOB
        +varchar email UK
        +varchar password
        +varchar primary_phone
        +varchar alternate_phone
        +int department_id FK
        +int year
        +int semester
        +varchar academic_year
        +enum status : active | dc | graduated
    }

    class courses {
        +int course_id PK
        +varchar course_code UK
        +varchar course_name
        +int department_id FK
        +int year
        +int semester
        +int teacher_id FK
    }

    class enrollments {
        +int enrollment_id PK
        +int student_id FK
        +int course_id FK
        +varchar academic_year
    }

    class timetable {
        +int timetable_id PK
        +int department_id FK
        +int semester
        +enum day
        +int slot_id FK
        +int course_id FK
    }

    class time_slots {
        +int slot_id PK
        +time start_time UK
        +time end_time
    }

    class attendance_sessions {
        +int session_id PK
        +int course_id FK
        +date session_date
        +int created_by FK
        +varchar academic_year
    }

    class attendance_records {
        +int record_id PK
        +int session_id FK
        +int student_id FK
        +enum status : present | absent
    }

    class student_fees {
        +int fee_id PK
        +int student_id FK
        +varchar academic_year
        +decimal total_fee
        +decimal paid_amount
    }

    class refresh_tokens {
        +int id PK
        +int user_id
        +enum user_type : student | faculty
        +varchar role
        +text token
        +datetime expires_at
    }

    department "1" --> "*" teachers : has
    department "1" --> "*" students : has
    department "1" --> "*" courses : offers
    department "1" --> "*" timetable : schedules
    teachers "1" --> "*" courses : teaches
    teachers "1" --> "*" attendance_sessions : creates
    students "1" --> "*" enrollments : enrolled_in
    courses "1" --> "*" enrollments : has
    courses "1" --> "*" timetable : scheduled_in
    courses "1" --> "*" attendance_sessions : has
    time_slots "1" --> "*" timetable : used_by
    attendance_sessions "1" --> "*" attendance_records : contains
    students "1" --> "*" attendance_records : has
    students "1" --> "*" student_fees : pays
```

