## 6. Activity Diagram — Student Promotion

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> Input["Admin selects:<br/>department_id, current_semester,<br/>new_academic_year"]
    Input --> Fetch["Fetch all active students<br/>in dept + semester"]
    Fetch --> BeginTx["BEGIN TRANSACTION"]
    BeginTx --> Loop{"For each student"}
    
    Loop --> Check{"semester == 8?"}
    
    Check -- Yes --> Graduate["UPDATE status = 'graduated'"]
    Graduate --> Next["Next student"]
    
    Check -- No --> CalcNew["newSemester = current + 1<br/>newYear = ceil(newSem / 2)"]
    CalcNew --> UpdateStudent["UPDATE student:<br/>semester, year, academic_year"]
    UpdateStudent --> GetCourses["SELECT courses for<br/>new semester + dept"]
    GetCourses --> HasCourses{"Courses found?"}
    
    HasCourses -- Yes --> Enroll["INSERT enrollments<br/>for each course"]
    Enroll --> CreateFee["INSERT student_fees<br/>(total_fee = 85000)"]
    CreateFee --> Next
    
    HasCourses -- No --> CreateFee
    
    Next --> Loop
    Loop -- All done --> Commit["COMMIT TRANSACTION"]
    Commit --> Response["Return success message"]
    Response --> End([End])
```

